values: so for about a week now i haven't been sleeping well again. it never fucking ends. if i do fall asleep it's for maybe an hour at a time and such a light sleep that it doesn't matter. i dunno how the hell i practiced yesterday in this shape. no idea what's going on today. no phone calls yet or anything. man, breaking up with people is tough. even if you don't like them in the slightest bit anymore. maybe it's because i'm used to being the one getting dumped or screwed over so bad that i get pissed and break it off. either way, it must be done today. why? because i said so. that's right all you uninterested ladies. i'll be back on the market so you can be all "so fucking what?" and it will rule. enough of how much today sucks. there are a few leafy fucks i miss and haven't talked to in forever. i wish i could make it back to london this summer. ah well. "007, what's your status?" "well the russian mercenary got away but i did manage to fuck a pair of hot blonde lab workers." "well done, 007." -dp-
